{"tid":497480,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"原來零晨自己一個走落街乜都唔諗係咁爽","createTime":"2017-12-12T21:18:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-14T16:30:15.000Z","uid":13385,"like":100,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"30cd6f875249cf8ca1ee3c35320bdfb2f52e185d","tid":497480,"uid":13385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T21:18:54.000Z","msg":"十幾度 落街 去7仔買杯粟米湯<br />\n明明就好凍 拎住杯湯 真係覺得好溫暖<br />\n你可能話我on9啦<br />\n有咩心事 心煩<br />\n咩都唔諗 <br />\n搵條樓梯 靜靜地坐下 聽下歌<br />\n<br />\n真係好撚正"},{"pid":"798a1882a3a11881777a91fce404a5fad58525ec","tid":497480,"uid":155732,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T21:23:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/12.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e709df6425ead99b3d3f8f2dcc3067068e4026f","tid":497480,"uid":3908,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T21:30:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"852df40ef78a96224015a0353ee886847cb9b867","tid":497480,"uid":151061,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T21:33:13.000Z","msg":"真心正 成日打通宵機 落街買野食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9545059067f510f64c74f48346df1934d808f163","tid":497480,"uid":13385,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T21:33:24.000Z","msg":"唔識表達個種正有幾正<br />\n好似全世界冇晒人咁 <br />\n可能因為太夜<br />\n下次試下去海邊先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bc4fd2f72731264f00cbdededb5a842b7b8fc46","tid":497480,"uid":13385,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T21:34:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真心正 成日打通宵機 落街買野食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n買完野食就上樓食唔計呀 <br />\n你都冇靜坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"